      "created_at": "2019-04-27T12:52:41.815Z",
      "cooked": "<p>o intelektual i modh, gjithe kete kohe qe ke munguar dhe jevgu ka lare kembet ne kanalet e ujrave te zezaq, ke studjuar libra per te gjetur se si perkthehet titulli i instalacionit te pare ne bote? Se heret e fundit qe ke komentuar e perktheve “arke me shishe birre”? Pranej s’je dukur me kendej pari, prej turpit sepse kaqe gje e dine edhe jevgjit, e jo me intelektualet e mdhej qe perkthejne Jungun.</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox wikipedia\" data-onebox-src=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bottle_Rack\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bottle_Rack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">en.wikipedia.org</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    \n\n<h3><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bottle_Rack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Bottle Rack</a></h3>\n\n<p>The Bottle Rack (also called Bottle Dryer or Hedgehog) (Egouttoir or Porte-bouteilles or Hérisson)  is a proto-Dada artwork created in 1914 by Marcel Duchamp. Duchamp labeled the piece a \"readymade\", a term he used to describe his collection of ordinary, manufactured objects not commonly associated with art. The readymades did not have the serious tone of European Dada works, which criticized the violence of World War I, and instead focused on a more nonsensical nature, chosen purely on the ba Th...</p>\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Katror\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"4409\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/k/77aa72/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"><a href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/t/pakti-me-gjarperin-pjese-e-dyte/4409/2\">Pakti me Gjarpërin (pjesë e dytë)</a></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>…Si “Katrori” i Malevicit ashtu edhe “Arka e shisheve” e Duchamp jane gjeste simbolike qe nuk kane te bejne fare me artin ne kuptimin e ngushte te fjales. Megjithate ato shenojne dy ekstremet ( “abstraksionit te madh” dhe “realizmit te madh”) ndermjet te cilave te arti imagjinativ i dekadave ne vazhdim mund te rradhitet dhe kuptohet.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p><em><strong>“Arka e shisheve”</strong></em> <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/rofl.png?v=12\" title=\":rofl:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rofl:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/rofl.png?v=12\" title=\":rofl:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rofl:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/rofl.png?v=12\" title=\":rofl:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rofl:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
